## Cloud Wallet UI (Vite) environment variables

# Backend base URL (used by src/api/client.ts)
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Optional allowlist for accepting *plain https* QR payloads as credential-offer URLs.
# Comma-separated host[:port] entries (no scheme).
#
# When set, `parseCredentialOfferInput()` only accepts plain https URLs whose `url.host`
# is in this allowlist. `openid-credential-offer://...` links are still accepted normally.
#
# Example:
# VITE_ALLOWED_CREDENTIAL_OFFER_HOSTS=issuer.example.com,wallet.example.org,localhost:8080
# VITE_ALLOWED_CREDENTIAL_OFFER_HOSTS=

